<doc id="1011775" wikidata="Q4994169" url="?curid=1011775" title="Åsbo Northern Hundred">
<text>Åsbo Northern Hundred () was a hundred in Skåne in Sweden. Until the Treaty of Roskilde in 1658, it was Danish.

==See also==
