<doc id="1011823" wikidata="Q4994182" url="?curid=1011823" title="Åsbo Southern Hundred">
<text>Åsbo Southern Hundred () was a hundred of Skåne in Sweden. Until The Treaty of Roskilde in 1658, it was in Denmark.

== See also ==
*Åsbo Northern Hundred divided between Halland and Skåne
*List of hundreds of Sweden

