<doc id="1011984" wikidata="Q2671676" url="?curid=1011984" title="Vartofta">
<text>Vartofta is a locality situated in Falköping Municipality, Västra Götaland County, Sweden. It had 540 inhabitants in 2010.

&quot;Vartofta Hundred&quot;, or &quot;Vartofta härad&quot;, was a hundred divided between Småland and Västergötland in Sweden.

